                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Team Member 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden border-2 border-brand-700">
          <img src="/images/team-3.jpg" alt="Fr. Michael Collins" class="w-full h-64 object-cover object-center">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1">Fr. Michael Collins</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-700 font-medium mb-4">Parish Relations</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">As a former parish priest, Fr. Michael provides invaluable insights into the specific needs of parishes and ensures our solutions align with their practical realities.</p>
            <div class="flex space-x-3">
              <a href="#" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-brand-700">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
